{
  "text": "Cell culture and treatment with kaolin A549 (RIKEN Cell Bank, Tsukuba, Japan) and RAW264 (RIKEN Cell Bank) were maintained in MEM (Nacalai Tesque, Kyoto, Japan) supplemented with 10% fetal bovine serum, penicillin (100 U/mL) and streptomycin (0.1 mg/mL). The cells were cultured at 37\u00b0C in 5% CO [CITATION_1] . All experiments were performed with exponentially growing cells.",
